pullrequest.title: Fix clang warnings and Windows macro

content.raw: Instead of changing `OUT` to `T`, could it be made into `Out`? It's not surprising that an all-caps token would collide with a macro, but camelcase should be fine. And it's nice to keep template parameters descriptive instead of throwing around `T` everywhere.
